        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11466.6666667,
          "startTime": 11.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ついにラヴラビとお化け屋敷のコラボ当日ですね！\nお客さんも沢山待っていて、凄い盛り上がりです……！",
      "startTime": 6.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき行列に並んでいる人が話していたが\nラヴラビを知らない人もちらほらいるみたいだな",
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8000000794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "このコラボをきっかけにラヴラビのことを\n知ってもらえたらとても嬉しいですね！",
      "startTime": 20.5585805836,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7708.086186399999,
          "startTime": 28.26666677
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5333335876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "まずは開園前のリハーサルが\n無事に終わればいいんですが",
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、怜ちゃん！　それに琴乃ちゃんも\n今日は来てくれてありがとう！",
      "startTime": 33.2666663329,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8766.667000399999,
          "startTime": 42.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.633333667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そう、入り口はあっちだよ\n後で感想聞かせてね。いってらっしゃい！",
      "startTime": 39.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰かを呼びたいとは聞いていたが\n怜達のことだったんだな",
      "startTime": 45.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.4333359558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　怜ちゃんって\nとっても素敵な悲鳴を上げてくれるんです",
      "startTime": 49.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "前に私がプロデュースしたお化け屋敷に行った時も\n凄く反応が良くって",
      "startTime": 56.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7666718323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "一人じゃ不安だからって琴乃も連れて来ていたが\n琴乃も琴乃でお化け屋敷は苦手だったような……",
      "startTime": 62.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ～。映画通りの7怖ぐらいで\n怖さは調整しておきましたから！",
      "startTime": 70.5000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1000112692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、この日のために怜ちゃん達には事前に\n映画を観てきてもらったんです",
      "startTime": 77.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.6333446025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、とっても楽しんでくれるはずです！\nはぁ～、早く感想が聞きたいな～",
      "startTime": 83.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8333446025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だからあんなに怖がっていたのか……\n今にも泣きそうだったぞ",
      "startTime": 89.6136460031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ん……今の張り裂けんばかりの悲鳴って\nもしかしなくても怜達のものじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 96.0666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.633336385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "最高の悲鳴ですね。あんなに怖がってくれるなんて\n監修を頑張った甲斐がありました……！",
      "startTime": 104.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはどうですか？\nリハーサルに参加しませんか？",
      "startTime": 109.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1333323955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、俺はこの後予定している千紗の撮影と\nインタビューに備えないといけないから……",
      "startTime": 115.399995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.166667684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "まだ予定の時間には早いですよね？\nせっかくですし、体験していって下さい！",
      "startTime": 121.9333292644,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 126.6666625977
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.3333292644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "気遣いはありがたいが、俺は大丈夫……\nって、ど、どうして腕を掴むんだ！？",
      "startTime": 127.6666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.7333425681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "手伝ってくれた{user}さんに\nぜひ見せたいところがあるんです！",
      "startTime": 133.099995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3666718324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、リハーサルが終わっちゃう前に\n中に入っちゃいましょう……！",
      "startTime": 138.4666625977,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3299.9989827000036,
          "startTime": 141.7666615804
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3333.333333300004,
          "startTime": 141.799995931
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.499995931
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.499995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "前回来た時よりも不気味な雰囲気ですよね？\n照明の色とか明るさを調整してもらったんです",
      "startTime": 146.9666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かに、同じお化け屋敷のはずなのに\n雰囲気が違うな……わっ！？",
      "startTime": 154.399995931,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5083.330202100001,
          "startTime": 156.0166625977
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10733.333333399998,
          "startTime": 165.1333292644
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knife-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11100.004068999993,
          "startTime": 165.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.7666657289
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "今のはお茶会に遅れないように走る兎さんです\n原作通り目が飛び出してるんですよ！",
      "startTime": 162.299995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_13_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "あっちにいるのはタコ頭の騎士さんです\n馬も含めて、模型を作ってくれたんです",
      "startTime": 169.6666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
